metadata.name: Flyer
metadata.description:
I travel the sky. Even I, who love my tainted homeland, have finally decided to travel the galaxy.
The universe is bigger than I thought, and I am not sure I will find my next home in the time I have left to live.
I'm just amazed that there are so many civilizations that are more developed than my home.
Long, long in the future, I will use my life to travel the universe to find a home where my descendants can live in peace.
Until that time comes, we will continue to communicate with each other forever. Where shall I go next?
